sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(EPP) 9002/TCP gRPC
    participant Prefill as Prefill vLLM<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Sidecar as routing-sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Decode as Decode vLLM<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, HF: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Optimized Baseline)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc request<br/>gRPC/9002
    Note right of EPP: Scoring plugins:<br/>queue depth, KV cache util,<br/>prefix cache hit rate
    EPP-->>GW: Selected backend
    GW->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80

    Note over Client, HF: Flow 2: Prefill/Decode Disaggregated Inference
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc request<br/>gRPC/9002 (prefill profile)
    EPP-->>GW: Selected prefill instance
    GW->>Prefill: Prefill request<br/>HTTP/8000
    Note over Prefill, Decode: KV Cache Transfer
    Prefill->>Decode: NIXL KV transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA/TCP<br/>No encryption (L2)
    Sidecar->>Decode: Decode trigger<br/>HTTP/8200
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80 via Gateway

    Note over Client, HF: Flow 3: Wide Expert-Parallelism (Multi-Node)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc request<br/>gRPC/9002
    EPP-->>GW: Selected leader pod
    GW->>Sidecar: Forward to leader<br/>HTTP/8000
    Sidecar->>Decode: Leader vLLM<br/>HTTP/8200
    Note over Decode: LeaderWorkerSet topology
    Decode->>Decode: Worker RPC<br/>5555/TCP (data parallel)
    Decode->>Decode: NVSHMEM/NCCL collective<br/>IB/RoCE RDMA (L2)
    Decode->>Decode: NIXL KV transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA/TCP
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80

    Note over Client, HF: Model Loading (Startup)
    Decode->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>Decode: Model artifacts
